snippet.title: Lords of the Fallen - Official Extended Story Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Enter the dark fantasy world of Lords of the Fallen and learn more about the story in this brutal new trailer for the upcoming action RPG. Lords of the Fallen will be available on PC, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series X/S on October 13.

#IGN #Gaming #LordsOfTheFallen
